msgid "Scenario V: Return to A Phantom of Truth"
msgstr "冒险V：重返真相幻影"

msgid "Randomly put 1 of each of the following locations into play: Montmarte, Opéra Garnier, Montparnasse, Grand Guignol, Père Lachaise Cemetery, Canal Saint-Martin, Notre-Dame, Le Marais, and Gardens of Luxembourg. Remove the other versions of those locations from the game."
msgstr "在以下各地点之中每个地点各随机选择1张，将所选地点放置入场：蒙马特尔、加尼叶歌剧院、蒙巴纳斯、大木偶剧场、拉雪兹神父公墓、圣马丁运河、巴黎圣母院、玛黑区、卢森堡公园。将这些地点的其他所有版本移出游戏。"

msgid "Put Gare d’Orsay into play. Each investigator begins play at Gare d’Orsay."
msgstr "将奥赛火车站放置入场。每位调查员从奥赛火车站开始游戏。"

msgid "Set the double‐sided The Organist enemy and both copies of Figure in the Shadows aside, out of play."
msgstr "将双面风琴手敌人、2张影中身形放在一边，位于场外。"

msgid ""
"For the duration of this scenario, the following additional rules apply:\n"
"\"<b>Forced</b> - After The Organist enters play: Shuffle both set-aside copies of Figure in the Shadows into the encounter deck, along with the encounter discard pile.\"\n"
"Attach the Return to A Phantom of Truth scenario reference card to the scenario reference card as a reminder."
msgstr ""
"在本场冒险接下来的时间里，增加以下额外规则：\n"
"“<b>强制</b> - 在风琴手入场后：将遭遇弃牌堆和放在一边的两张影中身形洗入遭遇牌堆。”\n"
"将重返真相幻影冒险辅助卡叠加到冒险辅助卡，以作提示。"
